        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Tribal Addiction and Recovery Act of 2018 or the TARA Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to&nbsp;give Indian tribes and tribal organizations access to the opioid grant program designated for the state response to the opioid crisis. </p>]]></text>
